A car bomb has killed at least 8 people outside a restaurant that is opposite a the Internal security Ministry headquarters. At the scene of the explosion in Mogadishu's Shangani district the bodies of the dead were strewened to the ground as the vehicle involved was up in flames. The location is also near the Sports Ministry heaequaters.No group has claimed responsibility for the attack although in the past similar attacks have been linked to the insurgency group Alshabaab.